            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="grc">
                <ab>
                   <lb n="1"/> Ὁ <persName type="divine" key="God"><name nymRef="#Θεός"></name><w lemma="Θεός"><expan><abbr rend="supraline">Θ</abbr><ex>εό</ex><abbr rend="supraline">ς<am>`</am></abbr></expan></w></persName>,                   
                    <lb n="2"/><choice><orig>ο</orig><reg>ὁ</reg></choice> <persName type="divine" key="God"><name nymRef="#Θεός"></name><w lemma="Θεός"><expan><abbr rend="supraline">Θ</abbr><ex>εὸ</ex><abbr rend="supraline">ς<am>`</am></abbr></expan></w></persName> <w lemma="ἐγώ"><expan><abbr rend="supraline"><hi rend="ligature">ἡμ</hi>ῶ</abbr><ex>ν</ex></expan></w>
                    <lb n="3"/>ὁ <w><choice><sic>τὼν</sic><corr>τὸν</corr></choice></w> <w lemma="οὐράνιος"><choice><choice><sic>ο<choice><orig>ὑ</orig><reg>ὐ</reg></choice><lb n="4" break="no"/>ράνιων</sic><corr>οὐ<lb n="4" break="no"/>ράνιον</corr></choice></choice></w>
                    <lb n="5"/><w lemma="ἄρτος"><choice><sic><choice><orig>ά</orig><reg>ἄ</reg></choice>ρτων</sic><corr>ἄρτον</corr></choice></w> <hi rend="ligature">τ<choice><orig>η</orig><reg>ὴ</reg></choice></hi>ν 
                    <lb n="6"/><w lemma="τροφή"><expan><abbr rend="supraline">τροφ</abbr><ex>ὴν</ex></expan></w>
                 </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
               <p>Pending</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>O God, our God, who sent the Heavenly Bread, the food (of the whole world)</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The omicron at the beginning of the text inscribing an abstract cross, is probably influenced by the decorative art of the manuscripts. The inscription is from the Prayer of the Prothesis. 
</p>
            </div>
